- [Creative Commons  CC BY-SA 4.0](https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/)  
- [ICRC  Geneva Conventions IV, Art. 23](https://ihl-databases.icrc.org/en/ihl-treaties/gciv-1949/article-23)  
